                    <span>Extremely easy to read.  Every point is supported by real life examples or funny bloopers.  Because of its simplicity, it sticks and you are more likely to apply it to your next presentation, speech, delivering a status to the boss.  It is worth having in the bookshelf as a business reference or for personal situations.</span>
                  
              
